{"data":[{"date":"09:08 18/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: HLV Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2016/1/7/HLV-Zidane-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-hinh-anh-2.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c sau khi chia tay Real Madrid. V\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zizou s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB Juventus.\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gi\u00fap Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, k\u1ebft th\u00fac qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n 3 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zidane Ronaldo\" title=\"Zidane Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/5/29/Zidane Ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Zidane - Ronaldo s\u1eafp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Juve?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 r\u00fat lui c\u1ee7a Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4n ngoan khi m\u00e0 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez c\u0169ng \u0111ang m\u1ea5t d\u1ea7n ni\u1ec1m tin \u1edf nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i La Liga kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng \u2018b\u1ecb l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean\u2019, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a Libertad Digital, v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho CLB Juventus v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 l\u00e0m c\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 3 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juventus chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Champions League, danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c HLV Zidane \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m. S\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n ra \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c sau 7 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-dung-ghep-ten-toi-voi-zidane-421-191124.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/griezmann-dung-ghep-ten-toi-voi-zidane.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-dung-ghep-ten-toi-voi-zidane-421-191124.html\">Griezmann: \u201c\u0110\u1eebng gh\u00e9p t\u00ean t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Zidane\u201d</span><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch th\u00fa khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t cho bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cGrizou\u201d nh\u1eb1m so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Zinedine Zidane.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-hlv-julen-lopetegui-cua-real-madrid-chat-xuc-tac-cho-cong-cuoc-chuyen-giao-the-he-o-bernabeu-180-188410.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/tan-hlv-julen-lopetegui-cua-real-madrid-chat-xuc-tac-cho-cong-cuoc-chuyen-giao-the-he-o-bernabeu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-hlv-julen-lopetegui-cua-real-madrid-chat-xuc-tac-cho-cong-cuoc-chuyen-giao-the-he-o-bernabeu-180-188410.html\">Julen Lopetegui: Ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c cho c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n giao th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 \u1edf Bernabeu</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane nh\u01b0ng sau ba n\u0103m no n\u00ea vinh quang, \u0111i\u1ec1u CLB...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-toi-khong-roi-real-de-dan-dat-dt-phap-184-188280.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/zidane-toi-khong-roi-real-de-dan-dat-dt-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-toi-khong-roi-real-de-dan-dat-dt-phap-184-188280.html\">Zidane: T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nHLV Zidane l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u00fd do chia tay Real cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4332","checkdouble":"191479"},{"date":"09:34 18/07","title":"Thai League t\u0103ng su\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ASEAN: Tham v\u1ecdng h\u1ecdc theo Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/18/world-cup-ket-thuc-roi-con-chut-gi-de-nho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2019, Thai League s\u1ebd t\u0103ng su\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ASEAN ra s\u00e2n l\u00ean th\u00e0nh con s\u1ed1 3 v\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng h\u1ecdc theo m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Premier League.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thai League t\u0103ng su\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ASEAN<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT), \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Thai League v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ASEAN t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Thai League 2019 s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng su\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ASEAN ra s\u00e2n l\u00ean th\u00e0nh con s\u1ed1 3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thai League tang suat cau thu ASEAN ke tu mua giai toi.\" title=\"Th\u00e1i League t\u0103ng su\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ASEAN k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/world-cup-ket-thuc-roi-con-chut-gi-de-nho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00e1i League t\u0103ng su\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ASEAN k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Thai League 2019 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p tung ra s\u00e2n 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng l\u00fac. H\u1ea1n ng\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y g\u1ed3m 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ASEAN, 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i ch\u00e2u \u00c1. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecdc theo Premier League<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Somyot Poompanmoung, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FAT chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111ang thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1edbi, ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp theo nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Premier League ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn gi\u00fap c\u00e1c CLB ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Mu\u1ed1n Th\u00e1i Lan tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1eebng s\u1ee3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecba m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, vi\u1ec7c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng h\u1ea1n ng\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i n\u00e2ng cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng su\u1ea5t ASEAN c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Thai League s\u1ebd h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u1edf c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, FAT c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh chung s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i Lan khi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Thai League:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/cau-thu-viet-nam-co-kha-nang-tro-thanh-noi-binh-o-thai-league-291-187283.html\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ed9i binh \u1edf Thai League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-sao-binh-duong-bo\u0301ng-da\u0301-tha\u0301i-lan-da\u0309ng-ca\u0301p-cao-hon-vie\u0323t-nam-168-182549.html\">C\u1ef1u sao B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: Bo\u0301ng \u0111a\u0301 Tha\u0301i Lan \u0111\u0103\u0309ng c\u00e2\u0301p cao h\u01a1n Vi\u00ea\u0323t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/vleague-thai-league-va-cau-chuyen-so-doi-291-177651.html\">V-League, Thai League v\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/thai-league-2018-co-5-doi-xuong-hang-de-tang-chat-luong-291-177638.html\">Thai League 2018 c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ngan-vleague-thu-thanh-van-lam-sap-sang-thai-league-168-176404.html\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n s\u1eafp sang Thai League?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-muon-cong-phuong-sang-choi-bong-168-176234.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4331","checkdouble":"191486"},{"date":"10:31 18/07","title":"HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Roberto Martinez khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Eden Hazard n\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27, thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 an t\u1ecda \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard c\u0169ng v\u1eady, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga gi\u00fap anh gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng B\u1ea1c cao qu\u00fd sau Luka Modric.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV B\u1ec9 khuy\u00ean Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV B\u1ec9 khuy\u00ean Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng c\u00e0ng v\u00ec ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf m\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u00f3ng s\u1ed1t trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Sau khi Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede Bernabeu, anh s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh Cristiano Ronaldo sau khi si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha k\u1ebft th\u00fac 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Roberto Martinez tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid: \u201cEden n\u00ean v\u1eady b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. Real Madrid ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ebf ch\u1ebf xoay quanh Eden.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Eden nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean \u2018\u0111\u1ed5i gi\u00f3\u2019, t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m m\u1edbi m\u00ecnh n\u00ean t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Eden chia tay nhau, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Eden Hazard c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u0169ng v\u00ec l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u2013 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\">N\u00f3ng: Hazard \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u1ed1t d\u1ebbo c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 2-0 Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4330","checkdouble":"191484"},{"date":"11:28 18/07","title":"James Rodriguez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/25/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u1eddi Bernabeu 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nJames chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u1ec1 Real<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi CLB, v\u00e0 c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ed1 d\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a James &ndash; \u00f4ng Juan Carlos Restrepo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, r\u1eb1ng HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 tu\u1ea7n, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi nhau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang ph\u00e2n t\u00edch nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt &ndash; James Rodriguez ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Zidane r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Real Madrid tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn. Xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng James s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\" title=\"James Rodriguez s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua 1 n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich, m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng, James s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cam k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Bayern, nh\u01b0ng khi Real Madrid m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra&rdquo; &ndash; b\u1ed1 d\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a James v\u1edbi Bayern Munich s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6/2019, cho ph\u00e9p H\u00f9m x\u00e1m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u euro khi th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng James Rodriguez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Cris Ronaldo, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale. H\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i James l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nHLV Roberto Martinez khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Eden Hazard n\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27, thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 an t\u1ecda \u1edf m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/7/HLV-Zidane-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/zidane-sap-tai-ngo-ronaldo-tai-juve-176-191479.html\">N\u00d3NG: HLV Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus</span><br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c sau khi chia tay Real Madrid. V\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zizou s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4329","checkdouble":"191502"},{"date":"11:52 18/07","title":"Luis Enrique t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga lo\u1ea1i ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f4i ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t sinh ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c, khi HLV Julen Lopetegui b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc sau khi ngang nhi\u00ean \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi Real Madrid.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique c\u1ee7a TBN t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft \u0110TQG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique c\u1ee7a TBN t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft \u0110TQG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-la-lua-chon-dung-dan-cho-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique c\u1ee7a TBN t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft \u0110TQG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau khi c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, L\u0110B\u0110 La Roja l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u1eaft tay t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, Luis Enrique ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng. HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i t\u00ean xa l\u1ea1 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u khi t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng Barcelona, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00fa \u0103n ba l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga, Copa del Rey v\u00e0 Champions League \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2014-15.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Luis Enrique tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng bao l\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm l\u1ea5y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat do d\u1ef1, c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc. D\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi n\u00e0y r\u1ed3i, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nghe theo ai hay \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i n\u00e0o h\u1ebft. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Luis Enrique s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Wembley ng\u00e0y 8/9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Anh. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft cho HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Euro 2020 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eb1m g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1ee9 ba trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-190800.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luis-enrique-la-lua-chon-dung-dan-cho-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-190812.html\">Luis Enrique l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4328","checkdouble":"191508"},{"date":"10:14 18/07","title":"Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/25/arsenal-da-co-chu-ky-tuyet-voi-nhat-mua-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 5 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Robert Pires ca ng\u1ee3i HLV Unai Emery m\u1edbi l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nEmery l\u00e0 \u201ct\u00e2n binh\u201d s\u1ed1 1<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi HLV Arsene Wenger ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi b\u1ecf chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, BL\u0110 Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Sau c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t Unai Emery \u2013 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi b\u1ecb PSG ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 ngay khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng, HLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t l\u00fac 5 t\u00e2n binh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. So s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d, khi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi s\u1eafm bom t\u1ea5n \u2013 vi\u1ec7c mua b\u00e1n n\u0103m nay c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd\u2026 ph\u00e1t ho\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, bao g\u1ed3m Lucas Torreira, Matteo Guendouzi, Bernd Leno, Sokratis Papastathopoulos v\u00e0 Stephan Lichsteiner. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Robert Pires c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pires ca ng\u1ee3i HLV Unai Emery l\u00e0 bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pires ca ng\u1ee3i HLV Unai Emery l\u00e0 bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/arsenal-da-co-chu-ky-tuyet-voi-nhat-mua-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pires ca ng\u1ee3i HLV Unai Emery</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u201cTheo t\u00f4i, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Arsenal th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Unai Emery. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh. Nh\u01b0ng Emery \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng.\u201d</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u00d4ng \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf Ph\u00e1p, s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Arsenal\u201d \u2013 Pires ca ng\u1ee3i HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Emery \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam bom t\u1ea5n \u2013 v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 ngay \u1edf 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, v\u1edbi 2 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech-172-191487.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/5/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech-172-191487.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 t\u1eeb Arsenal</span><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Daily Mail, CLB Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Petr Cech tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi tranh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/welbeck-va-ospina-sap-bi-hlv-emery-tong-khoi-arsenal-172-191482.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/welbeck-va-ospina-sap-bi-hlv-emery-tong-khoi-arsenal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/welbeck-va-ospina-sap-bi-hlv-emery-tong-khoi-arsenal-172-191482.html\">Welbeck v\u00e0 Ospina s\u1eafp b\u1ecb HLV Emery t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ecfi Arsenal</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Danny Welbeck v\u00e0 David Ospina, HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4327","checkdouble":"191491"},{"date":"10:26 18/07","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea n\u1ebfu \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/chelsea-san-sang-chia-tay-cahill.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, trung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Gary Cahill\u00a0s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Cahill s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Cahill s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/chelsea-san-sang-chia-tay-cahill.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Trung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea n\u1ebfu \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1eeb Bolton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2012, trung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, khi m\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m v\u00ec l\u00fd do tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, Cahill \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 27 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Cahill c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi ph\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u201cS\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu khi b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00ec b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 song th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, Gary Cahill c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ednh t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Theo t\u1edd Evening Standard, trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, trung v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HLV Sarri c\u0169ng \u0111ang s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 The Blues. V\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Daniele Rugani. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Juve, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Rugani l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Rugani c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri khi hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chung \u1edf Empoli.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-conte-sap-ve-ac-milan-sau-khi-chia-tay-chelsea-172-191485.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/hlv-conte-sap-ve-ac-milan-sau-khi-chia-tay-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-conte-sap-ve-ac-milan-sau-khi-chia-tay-chelsea-172-191485.html\">HLV Conte s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u00dd, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u00ecnh b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi b\u1ecb CLB Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech-172-191487.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/5/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech-172-191487.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 t\u1eeb Arsenal</span><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Daily Mail, CLB Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Petr Cech tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi tranh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-nai-ni-nhung-tru-cot-o-lai-chelsea-172-191488.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/19/hlv-sarri-nai-ni-nhung-tru-cot-o-lai-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-nai-ni-nhung-tru-cot-o-lai-chelsea-172-191488.html\">HLV Sarri n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn, t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4326","checkdouble":"191493"},{"date":"10:19 18/07","title":"MU l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ivan Perisic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/mu-lam-dieu-nay-de-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-ivan-perisic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1ee7 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t Ivan Perisic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua do Juan Mata \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Perisic \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Perisic \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/mu-lam-dieu-nay-de-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-ivan-perisic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n MU mua Perisic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i M.U c\u00f3 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Sanchez, Martial v\u00e0 Rashford. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Perisic\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ivan-perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-mu-cua-mourinho-172-191400.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Inter Milan. \u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n gi\u00e1ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Perisic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1ee7 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perisic toi Man United\" title=\"Perisic toi Man United\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/2/Ivan-Perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-MU-cua-Mourinho--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Perisic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, M.U \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cho Perisic, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35, 44 v\u00e0 48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Inter Milan t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00f2i 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U v\u1eabn\u00a0 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua Perisic, Inter \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Mourinho c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 kinh ph\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Perisic, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Anthony Martial, c\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea \u0111ang nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Eden Hazard, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4325","checkdouble":"191494"},{"date":"10:45 18/07","title":"Kante \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/kante-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Kante ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y N'Golo Kante l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. D\u00f9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Kante ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Kante ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/15/Tuong-lai-Kante-phu-thuoc-hoan-toan-vao-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap Leicester v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f9ng The Blues mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. \u1ede World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh Kante l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante-172-190952.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante</span>, Barca c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi PSG, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Thiago Motta, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 36. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Barca, vi\u1ec7c Paulinho v\u00e0 Iniesta ra \u0111i bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Kante v\u00ec th\u1ebf tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Kante ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Kante ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" title=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/kante-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai NGolo Kante ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 80 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 PSG v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, n\u1ebfu Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y Kante s\u1ebd t\u1edbi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed ho\u1eb7c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu The Blues ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef Kante \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Theo Mirror, t\u00e2n HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Kante \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Kante v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. \u1ede b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ef1u sao Leicester s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4324","checkdouble":"191496"},{"date":"10:59 18/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 18/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-1807.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i \u1edf, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 18/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Kante ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1807 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1807 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-1807-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>NGolo Kante \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Kante ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kante-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-172-191496.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-1807-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kante-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-172-191496.html\">Kante \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Kante ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Morata c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh AC Mian \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata. HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, song Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Real n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Gary Cahill s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0 West Ham, Southampton hay Wolves mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 mua Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" title=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mua Willian </span>v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i g\u1eedi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Barca, t\u00e2n HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Liverpool v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Liverpool trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 Eden Hazard, Willian, Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 N'Golo Kante \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-nai-ni-nhung-tru-cot-o-lai-chelsea-172-191488.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/19/hlv-sarri-nai-ni-nhung-tru-cot-o-lai-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-nai-ni-nhung-tru-cot-o-lai-chelsea-172-191488.html\">HLV Sarri n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn, t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois co mot tran dau xuat sac\" title=\"Courtois c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Chelsea-muon-mua-Kasper-Schmeichel-thay-Courtois-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Real Madrid, theo \u0111\u00f3 Los Blancos s\u1ebd chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea kh\u00f4ng thu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Higuain</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Morata v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Giroud \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4323","checkdouble":"191503"},{"date":"07:05 18/07","title":"T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Ph\u00e1p dab c\u00f9ng Pogba trong l\u1ec5 m\u1eebng c\u00f4ng","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/tong-thong-phap-dab-cung-pogba-trong-le-mung-cong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u00d4ng Emmanuel Macron t\u1ecf ra th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi tr\u1ebb c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p v\u1eeba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2>H\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Paris c\u00f9ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. C\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 500.000 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Champs-\u00c9lys\u00e9es \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd chi\u1ebfc xe bus ch\u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111i qua. Sau khi giao l\u01b0u v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, HLV Deschamps v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf ph\u1ee7 T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng, nh\u1eadn huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng B\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea9u B\u1ed9i tinh t\u1eeb T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Macron.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/phap-10-1531837221382161279801-15318372710001999659593.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng \u00f4ng Macron t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n m\u1eadt v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i. Paul Pogba, kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat e d\u00e8, c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u00f4ng Macron th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c dab bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Man Utd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u00f4ng Macron ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p r\u1ea5t \u0103n \u00fd, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng Macron \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng &quot;\u0111\u1ed1n tim&quot; ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. \u00d4ng c\u00f9ng T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i. Khi Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u00f4ng Macron \u0103n m\u1eebng cu\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lan truy\u1ec1n r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u00f4ng Macron v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i Croatia chia bu\u1ed3n v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0103n m\u1eebng r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4322","checkdouble":"191473"},{"date":"08:43 18/07","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/19/hlv-le-thuy-hai-noi-gi-ve-danh-sach-tap-trung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng n\u00ean g\u1ecdi th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 17/7, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\" target=\"_blank\">danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam </span>\u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 26 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 v\u00e0 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean 23 g\u1ed3m \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng Park n\u00ean g\u1ecdi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam mat co hoi doi dau nguoi Uc\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/croatia-viet-tiep-cau-chuyen-20-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7n g\u1ecdi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng Olympic VN</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng cho hay: &quot;Theo t\u00f4i, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 sau v\u00f2ng 20, V.League 2018 xem th\u1eed c\u00f3 th\u00eam g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt hay kh\u00f4ng r\u1ed3i g\u1ecdi th\u00eam t\u1eeb 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. \u0110\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u1ea1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd danh s\u00e1ch r\u1ed3i ch\u1ed1t 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed9n. L\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i &ldquo;l\u01a1&rdquo; c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng Park c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, th\u00ec nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb CLB n\u00e0o, hay CLB th\u00ec 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi nh\u01b0ng CLB kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1. G\u1ecdi ai v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. \u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang ta quan t\u00e2m l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 n\u00e0o, ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n ra sao \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cao nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;, HLV L\u00ea Thu\u1ef5 H\u1ea3i cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 25/7 t\u1edbi 3/9/2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD.</p>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (FLC Thanh H\u00f3a), \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh (Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC), Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (SLNA), Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh, L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy (HAGL), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i (Viettel), Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (HAGL), L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c (SLNA)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (HAGL), Ho\u00e0ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n (Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh), H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng), Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh (B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-guong-mat-bi-hlv-park-hang-seo-bo-quen-tai-asiad-2018-168-191462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/10/1/hang-thu-dtvn-can-lam-bong-dang-mot-nhu-thanh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-guong-mat-bi-hlv-park-hang-seo-bo-quen-tai-asiad-2018-168-191462.html\">Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u00e9m duy\u00ean ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong-168-191451.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong-168-191451.html\">Sao b\u1ef1 Tottenham c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4321","checkdouble":"191477"},{"date":"07:56 18/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 18/7: \u201cG\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng\u201d World Cup ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-187-gang-tay-vang-world-cup-tien-sat-toi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 18/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Boca Juniors mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Barca. </strong>Boca Juniors r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Colombia. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Argentina m\u1edbi g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t t\u1edbi Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Courtois ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real Madrid. </strong>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Thibaut Courtois \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111o\u1ea1t G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 187 Courtois ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 187 Courtois ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/world-cup-2018-khep-lai-voi-nhung-danh-hieu-ca-nhan-xung-dang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Courtois</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Blind ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ajax. </strong>Man United x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 14 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chia tay sau 4 n\u0103m, Blind c\u00f9ng M.U \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 1 c\u00fap FA, 1 c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n v\u00e0 1 Europa League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Alisson.</strong> Liverpool \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi Alisson khi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd n\u1eb1m \u1edf cu\u1ed9c th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 AS Roma. Liverpool \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 72 tri\u1ec7u Euro (62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u1edbt l\u1edd Bayern.</strong> Jordan Pickford m\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 \u0110\u1ee9c, Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Everton. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, gi\u00fap \u0110TQG l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Pickford\" title=\"thu mon Pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/David-Moyes-phat-bieu-ve-Jordan-Pickford-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Everton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1eb9 Ronaldo: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc&rdquo;.</strong> Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u00e0 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a CR7 c\u0169ng m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>&ldquo;Brazil c\u1ee7a Tite v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i&rdquo;.</strong> Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Tite c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c CSKA \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. </strong>CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Evgeniy Giner, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CSKA Moscow x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4320","checkdouble":"191475"}]}